org.mobicents.slee.container.deployment.jboss
Class SleeContainerDeployerImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.mobicents.slee.container.AbstractSleeContainerModule
      org.mobicents.slee.container.deployment.jboss.SleeContainerDeployerImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
InternalDeployer, SleeContainerDeployer, SleeContainerModule
public class SleeContainerDeployerImpl
extends AbstractSleeContainerModule
implements InternalDeployer, SleeContainerDeployer

The SLEE module responsible for persistent deployments. It complements the JMX MBeans provided by the SLEE spec, providing "automated" (de)activations of components in DUs, and is able to hold a deployment till all its dependencies are deployed.

Author:
martins
